From {{af|en|loupe|t1=opening in a wall|hole|lang1=enm}}, from a {{der|en|gem}} source. Compare {{cog|ML.|loupa|loupa, lobia}} and {{cog|dum|lupen|t=to watch}}.<ref>{{R:Etymonline}}</ref>

